article.description: Teshaun Hightower posted 15 points as Tulane topped Alcorn State 68-57 on Monday night.
article.headline: Hightower scores 15 to lead Tulane over Alcorn St. 68-57
article.linkText: Hightower scores 15 to lead Tulane over Alcorn St. 68-57
article.story: NEW ORLEANS -- Teshaun Hightower posted 15 points as Tulane topped Alcorn State 68-57 on Monday night. Nic Thomas had 13 points for Tulane (8-2), which earned its fifth straight home victory. Jordan Walker added 11 points and Christion Thompson had 10. Corey Tillery had 21 points for the Braves (3-6) and Maurice Howard added 18. Tulane matches up against Akron on Friday. Alcorn State takes on Ecclesia at home on Friday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
